{"title":"凸多边形","time_limit":5000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2345","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>逆时针给出<em>n</em>个凸多边形的顶点坐标，求它们交的面积</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行有一个整数<em>n</em>，表示凸多边形的个数，以下依次描述各个多边形。第i个多边形的第一行包含一个整数<em>m<sub>i</sub></em>，表示多边形的边数，以下<em>m<sub>i</sub></em>行每行两个整数，逆时针给出各个顶点的坐标。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>仅包含一个实数，表示相交部分的面积，保留三位小数</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>2</p>\n<p>6</p>\n<p>-2 0</p>\n<p>-1 -2</p>\n<p>1 -2</p>\n<p>2 0</p>\n<p>1 2</p>\n<p>-1 2</p>\n<p>4</p>\n<p>0 -3</p>\n<p>1 -1</p>\n<p>2 2</p>\n<p>-1 0</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>5.233</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>50%的数据满足：<em>n</em>=2</p>\n<p>100%的数据满足：2&lt;=<em>n</em>&lt;=10，3&lt;=<em>m<sub>i</sub></em>&lt;=50，每维坐标为[-1000,1000]内的整数</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}